ammaire=E2=80=9D BP est une suite de <i>subgrammars</i>, et qu=E2=80=99on p=
asse de l=E2=80=99une =C3=A0 l=E2=80=99autre quand plus aucune r=C3=A8gle n=
=E2=80=99est candidate. Je n=E2=80=99en vois pas de mention sur la page=C2=
=A0<a href=3D"https://roomi-fields.com/en/articles/derivation-rules-modes-b=
p3/" style=3D"font-size: 10.5pt;">https://roomi-fields.com/en/articles/deri=
vation-rules-modes-bp3/</a></div><div x-em-replyforwardheader=3D""><br /></=
div><div x-em-replyforwardheader=3D"">A +</div><div x-em-replyforwardheader=
